lead_paragraph: Andrew Bogut's complaints over his Rio accommodation have received more attention than his troublesome knee but both seemed fine on Saturday as Australia opened the Rio Games men's basketball tournament with an 87-66 win over France.

headline.print_headline: Basketball: Jovial Bogut Shines as Australia Beat France
